{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Kenapa Serial Netflix Marvel Diputus Satu Demi Satu?","content":"<p>Buat fans serial televisi dari Marvel Comics, layanan <em>streaming</em> televisi Netflix adalah sebuah ‘surga’.</p>\n<p>Dimulai dengan Marvel’s Daredevil (2015), Netflix menciptakan sebuah <em>universe</em> untuk para superheroes Marvel “kelas dua” yang tidak tertampung di <em>universe</em> film bioskop “Marvel Cinematic Universe” alias MCU.</p>\n<p>Hal ini sekaligus menantang dominasi DC Comics di <em>segment</em> serial TV superheroes yang berjalan kuat sejak serial “Arrow” ; diputar di channel CW sejak tahun 2012. “Arrowverse”, begitu sebutan <em>universe</em> serial TV DC Comics, terus berekspansi dengan penambahan tokoh-tokoh dari DC Comics; terkini akan muncul Batwoman di mini-seri spesial “Elseworlds” Desember 2018.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52319\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52319\" data-attachment-id=\"52319\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/01-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52319\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: VitalThrills)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/01-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52319\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: VitalThrills)</p></div></p>\n<p><em>Universe</em> Marvel buatan Netflix sendiri awalnya terlihat sangat menjanjikan.</p>\n<p>Daredevil mendapatkan sambutan meriah dari fans Marvel (dan bahkan DC Comics seperti saya). Rasa pahit dari film teatrikal gagal “Daredevil” (2003) yang dibintangi oleh Ben Affleck dulu hilang karena serial yang dibintangi oleh Charlie Cox ini. Melihat sambutan positif pasar, Netflix dan Marvel tentu saja bersemangat untuk mengembangkan <em>franchise</em> tersebut.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52320\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52320\" data-attachment-id=\"52320\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/02-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52320\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: BleedingCool)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/02-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52320\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: BleedingCool)</p></div></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jAy6NJ_D5vU\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Selepas Daredevil, Netflix lanjut dengan membuat serial Marvel’s Jessica Jones. Kisah tentang superhero cewek bermasalah serta pecandu alkohol yang mencari jati diri tersebut juga berakhir sukses meraih pasar.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52321\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52321\" data-attachment-id=\"52321\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/03-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52321\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: TheBottomLine)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/03-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52321\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: TheBottomLine)</p></div></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/nWHUjuJ8zxE\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Disusul kemudian dengan pembuatan Marvel’s Luke Cage. Luke Cage juga meraih sukses walau awalnya sempat diragukan (sebagian besar keraguan karena tokoh utamanya berkulit hitam yang merupakan minoritas).</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52322\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52322\" data-attachment-id=\"52322\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/04-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52322\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: YouTube)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/04-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52322\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: YouTube)</p></div></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ytkjQvSk2VA\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Kesuksesan Luke Cage bahkan membuka pintu untuk dibuatnya serial Marvel’s Iron Fist; berhubung di komik mereka merupakan rekan/partner dalam lini “Heroes for Hire”.</p>\n<p>Sayangnya sambutan yang diterima oleh Iron Fist tidak sehangat ‘saudara-saudaranya’. Banyak opini yang menyatakan kalau Iron Fist digarap dengan jelek. Tidak menarik. Dan dianggap sebagai yang paling lemah dari judul-judul serial Marvel Netflix yang sudah ditayangkan.</p>\n<p>Saya sendiri setuju dengan pendapat tersebut. Akting Finn Jones terasa tidak <em>inspiring</em> sama sekali sebagai Danny Rand alias <em>“Iron Fist from K’un L’un”</em>. Datar dan kering.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52323\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52323\" data-attachment-id=\"52323\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/05-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52323\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: OverThinkingIt)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/05-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52323\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: OverThinkingIt)</p></div></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/f9OKL5no-S0\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Tapi Marvel tidak menganggap hal itu sebagai masalah besar. Mereka malah melakukan serial khusus kolaborasi antar superheroes ini dalam mini-seri bertajuk Marvel’s The Defenders. Dimana ‘Daredevil’ Matt Murdock , Jessica Jones, ‘Power Man’ Luke Cage serta Danny Rand ‘Iron Fist’ bergabung, bersatu untuk menghadapi musuh yang sama. Mini-seri The Defenders disambut cukup baik oleh fans; setidaknya tidak seperti sambutan dingin yang diterima oleh Marvel’s Iron Fist sebelumnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52324\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52324\" data-attachment-id=\"52324\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/06-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52324\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: WhatsOnNetflix)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/06-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52324\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: WhatsOnNetflix)</p></div></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QNwjRfSldM0\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/marvels-defenders-vs-marvels-avengers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Marvel&#8217;s The Defenders vs Marvel&#8217;s The Avengers</a></strong></p>\n<p>Berhenti sampai disana? Tentu saja tidak. Marvel dan Netflix kembali beraksi. Kali ini mereka menciptakan Marvel’s The Punisher.</p>\n<p>Karakter The Punisher alias Frank Castle, yang sebelumnya muncul di Daredevil, dikembangkan ke serial tersendiri. Walau menurut saya pribadi hasilnya tidak buruk-buruk amat namun lebih greget melihat The Punisher saat beradu fisik (dan strategi) dengan Daredevil ketimbang melihat aksi dia di serialnya sendiri.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52325\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52325\" data-attachment-id=\"52325\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/07-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52325\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: LitReactor)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/07-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52325\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: LitReactor)</p></div></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/lIY6zFL95hE\" width=\"722\" height=\"406\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Saat Netflix dan Marvel mengumumkan di awal September 2018 kalau The Defender di-<em>cancel</em> alias tidak lagi dilanjutkan/dibuat, fans sedikit kaget namun menganggap hal tersebut wajar.</p>\n<p>The Defenders tidak se-prospek The Avengers dari MCU. Plus orang masih menyalahkan performa buruk Iron Fist sebelumnya. The Defenders di-<em>cancel</em>? Ya sudah. Toh kisah sebelumnya juga ideal untuk berhenti.</p>\n<p>Fans tidak melihat adanya kemungkinan buruk lain di masa depan di pengumuman dan rilis season ketiga Daredevil. Mereka bergembira menyambut season terbaru tersebut tanpa menyadari kalau itu adalah kali terakhir mereka akan melihat serial Marvel superheroes di Netflix.</p>\n<p>12 Oktober 2018, Netflix mengumumkan kalau mereka meng-<em>cancel</em> Marvel’s Iron Fist setelah dua season. Tidak akan ada lagi serial Iron Fist di Netflix.</p>\n<p>Fans sudah menduga hal ini; beberapa malah tertawa karena tahu cepat atau lambat Iron Fist akan kena depak dari televisi karena performa buruk mereka. Yang fans tidak duga serta antisipasi adalah rentetan <em>cancel</em> yang menyusul Iron Fist setelahnya.</p>\n<p>Marvel’s Luke Cage di-<em>cancel</em> lewat pengumuman tanggal 19 Oktober 2018. Hanya beberapa hari setelah berita <em>cancel</em> Iron Fist. Beberapa fans yang optimis menganggap “Oh! Keduanya mungkin bakal digabung satu dalam serial Heroes for Hire seperti di komik!”</p>\n<p>Pendapat yang wajar juga, sih. Karena memang di komik keduanya ada dalam serial yang sama: “Heroes for Hire”. Jadi jika keduanya di-<em>cancel</em> karena sendiri-sendiri, mungkin tujuannya untuk digabung?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52326\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52326\" data-attachment-id=\"52326\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/08-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"08-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52326\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"(Sumber: WhatsOnNetflix)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/08-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52326\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(Sumber: WhatsOnNetflix)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sayang berita yang muncul berikutnya malah membuat panik para fans serial Marvel di Netflix. Daredevil, yang notabene adalah <em>pioneer</em> di <em>universe</em> Marvel Netflix, juga menemui ‘ajal’ nya. Pengumuman <em>cancel</em> Daredevil dari Netflix terjadi 29 November 2018.</p>\n<p>Hal ini jelas tidak di duga dan diharapkan para fans. Namun tetap saja terjadi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52327\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52327\" data-attachment-id=\"52327\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/09-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"09-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52327\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"Netflix meng-cancel Daredevil (Sumber: Geek.Com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/09-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52327\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Netflix meng-cancel Daredevil (Sumber: Geek.Com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Saat ini yang belum diumumkan (secara resmi) kalau di-<em>cancel</em> tinggal Marvel’s Jessica Jones dan Marvel’s The Punisher. Namun sepertinya hanya soal waktu saja. Hal itu pasti terjadi. Tapi sebenarnya ada apa dengan gelombang <em>cancel</em> Marvel TV show di Netflix ini?</p>\n<p>Dugaan terkuat adalah karena Disney, sebagai pemilik (hampir) semua IP Marvel Comics, sedang bersiap-siap meluncurkan layanan <em>streaming</em> mereka sendiri: Disney+ alias “Disney Plus”.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_52328\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-52328\" data-attachment-id=\"52328\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/kenapa-serial-netflix-marvel-diputus-satu-demi-satu/attachment/10-marvel-netflix-series/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"10-marvel-netflix-series\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-52328\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-marvel-netflix-series.jpg\" alt=\"Layanan streaming Disney (Sumber: TheWaltDisneyCompany)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-marvel-netflix-series.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/10-marvel-netflix-series-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-52328\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Layanan streaming Disney (Sumber: TheWaltDisneyCompany)</p></div></p>\n<p>Secara hitung-hitungan bisnis, akan lebih menguntungkan buat Disney (dan Marvel) jika menyiarkan serial-serial superheroes mereka di ‘lapak sendiri’ seperti di Disney+ . Lebih hemat dan lebih terkontrol ketimbang di Netflix dimana Disney tidak punya kuasa/kendali.</p>\n<p>Dengan meletakkan semua program siar Marvel (film serta televisi) di Disney+ , pihak Disney akan punya kendali sepenuhnya.</p>\n<p>Walau secara teori bagus karena lebih terpusat, namun buat beberapa kalangan hal ini justru mencemaskan. Karena siapapun tahu kalau Disney selalu berorientasi pada hal-hal dan nilai-nilai kekeluargaan. Disney tidak dikenal atau identik dengan produk kekerasan. Sementara mereka yang nonton serial-serial Marvel di Netflix sudah tahu kalau serial-serial itu memiliki <em>rating</em> R alias dewasa; dengan adegan kekerasan dan seksual ada dimana-mana.</p>\n<p>Jika benar Disney+ akan jadi tempat baru serial-serial Marvel yang di-<em>cancel</em> oleh Netflix, besar kemungkinan serial-serial tersebut akan mengalami modifikasi besar-besaran agar dapat meraih rating “Semua Umur” seperti layaknya produk-produk Disney.</p>\n<p>Bisa bayangkan serial Daredevil tanpa darah dan kekerasan seperti yang terlihat di Netflix sebelumnya? Akan aneh banget!</p>\n<p>Memang berita di-<em>cancel</em>-nya berbagai serial televisi Marvel di Netflix bukan berarti sebuah kepastian kalau serial-serial tersebut akan muncul di Disney+ . Bisa jadi Marvel memang menyetop serial-serial itu untuk selamanya. Alias tidak lagi diproduksi. Tapi orang bodoh mana yang tega menyembelih angsa bertelur emas?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"7581c70e-ced8-5e3c-9a13-e3673c5470e5"}}}